title: life as newgame+

Fuko used to say that we as humanity have finished the survival mode of life and are now on a kind of newgame+.

In this spirit, culture would be a modpack, and money give you access to special DLC's.

Working a skill or living a particular lifestyle is like exploring new mods, you gain access to the content as you play along.



